btn-primary font-weight-bold font-size-18\">待遇や手当について詳しくはこちら</a>\n  </div>\n</div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-5\"><div class=\"card\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"card-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<img class=\"img-fluid w-100 mb-3 second\" src=\"https://www.okamura-industry.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/recruit/img/welfare3.png\" alt=\"待遇や手当について\"></div>\n  <div class=\"card-body\">\n    <h3 class=\"card-title text-main font-weight-bold text-center\">休暇制度について</h3>\n    <p class=\"card-text mb-4\">週休2日で年間休日は113日。産前産後休暇や育児休暇、介護休暇などの休暇制度についてご紹介します。</p>\n    <a href=\"https://www.okamura-industry.co.jp/recruit/work/welfare/#holiday\" class=\"arrow text-center d-block py-3 btn btn-primary font-weight-bold font-size-18\">休暇制度について詳しくはこちら</a>\n  </div>\n</div></div>\n\t\t\t</div></div></section>\n\t<section>\n\t\t<div id=\"data\" class=\"container anchor\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"pt-3\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"d-sm-none\"><img src=\"https://www.okamura-industry.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/recruit/img/statue.png\" alt=\"数字で見るOKAMURA\" class=\"img-fluid\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"d-none d-sm-inline\"><img src=\"https://www.okamura-industry.co.jp/recruit/wp-content/themes/recruit/img/statue_l.png\" alt=\"数字で見るOKAMURA\" class=\"img-fluid\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"col-12 text-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mt-5 mb-3 mt-sm-5 py-sm-4\">数字で見るOKAMURA</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row align-items-center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-6 my-5\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 text-center text-main\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-male gender-ratio\"></i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i class=\"fas fa-female gender-ratio\"></i>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"row no-gutters\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12\">\n